title: Utraqve fortuna moderate ferenda, vel de superbia ex rebus secundis plerumqve oriri solita cohibenda atqve reprimenda, nec non de animo rebus adversis afflicto qvadantenus erigendo dissertationes duæ philosophico-philologico-poëticæ ... submittere decrevi
author: Been, Hans Nielsen, 1646-1708
